  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        -  Successful daily wear of FDA Group I or IV soft contact lenses for at least one week.

          -  Vision correctable to 20/30.

          -  Normal eyes - no current ocular abnormalities that prevent successful contact lens
             wear.

          -  No corneal surgery within the past 12 months.

          -  No systemic disease that affects that eye or that could be worsened by the use of
             contact lenses or solutions.

          -  No over-the-counter or prescription ocular medication.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
